 how it's so well controlled, it's really mind blowing.

15:26.120 --> 15:29.760
 So in the first two months in the embryo or whatever,

15:29.760 --> 15:32.680
 the first few weeks, months,

15:32.680 --> 15:37.080
 so yeah, the building blocks are constructed.

