25:00.600 --> 25:02.200
 with that genetic code in it.

25:02.200 --> 25:05.800
 And you can ask, what is this genetic code doing

25:05.800 --> 25:08.760
 to some aspects of development of the brain?

25:08.760 --> 25:12.000
 And for the first time, you may come to solutions

25:12.000 --> 25:16.000
