25:16.000 --> 25:17.360
 So many questions around this.

25:17.360 --> 25:20.520
 So if you take this human stem cell

25:20.520 --> 25:23.360
 for that particular person with that genetic code,

25:23.360 --> 25:26.520
 how, and you try to build an organoid,

